[Student "S"]
{NORTH bids 4\C, showing \H support, 13+ points and a singleton 
or void in \Cs.

SOUTH first shows her \DA, then, when NORTH signs off, 
makes one more try by showing her \SA.

NORTH finally gets inspired and bids the slam.}

